 * <ol>
 *   <li>UTF-8 encoding of the JSON input into a confined Arena</li>
 *   <li>Downcall via the pre-resolved MethodHandle</li>
 *   <li>Extraction of the Rust-allocated result string</li>
 *   <li>Native {@code dm_string_free} call to release Rust memory</li>
 * </ol>
 *
 * <p>Architecture:
 * <pre>
 *   L3 domain API (DataModellingL3)
 *        ↓ delegates
 *   L2 FFI transport (DataModellingL2)   ← this class
 *        ↓ downcall
 *   {{ nativeLibrary }} (native Rust/C)
 * </pre>
 *
 * <p>Graceful degradation: all methods throw {@link UnsupportedOperationException}
 * when the native library is not loaded. Set system property
 * {@code -D{{ libraryPathProp }}=/path/to/{{ nativeLibrary }}} to enable native operations.
 *
 * @generated by ggen from ontology
 * @pattern WCP-NB-03 (data-modelling custom variant)
 * @see DataModellingL3
