    /**
     * Uniform helper: encodes {@code json} to UTF-8, calls the native function via
     * {@code mh}, extracts the result string, frees native memory, and returns the
     * UTF-8 decoded Java String.
     *
     * <p>All 55 data-modelling-sdk functions share this helper because they all follow
     * the same {@code char* → char*} C ABI.</p>
     *
     * @param mh   pre-resolved downcall handle for the target native function
     * @param json UTF-8 JSON request; must not be null
     * @return UTF-8 JSON response from the native library
     * @throws AssertionError if the native call fails or returns NULL
